
FUNCTION CreateSlide1 GLOBAL
    # Click into the first slide and type some text
    MouseAndKeyboard.MoveMouseToImage.ClickImage Images: [imgrepo['PPTBlankPresentation5']] SearchForImageOn: MouseAndKeyboard.SearchTarget.EntireScreen MousePositionOnImage: MouseAndKeyboard.PositionOnImage.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0 Tolerance: 10 MovementStyle: MouseAndKeyboard.MovementStyle.AnimateFast Occurence: 1 Timeout: 5 ClickType: MouseAndKeyboard.ClickType.LeftClick SecondsBeforeClick: 0 SearchAlgorithm: MouseAndKeyboard.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy

    Scripting.RunPowershellScript Script: $'''$workstationname = hostname
Write-Output $workstationname''' ScriptOutput=> PSHostname ScriptError=> ScriptError
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''System Report %CurrentDateTime%''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
END FUNCTION
